<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-68-0236 </DOCNO><TEXT>This booklet compliments the textbook 'Fundamentals of chemistry' andis meant for advanced students of chemistry. It gives an introductioninto the composition, upgrading and combustion of fossile fuels and theircombustible products, the characteristics of automotive fuels and divisioninto physical and chemical properties of lubricants. Environmental questionsare briefly touched upon. One part relates to practical issues and dealswith the determination of important characteristic data. Each chapteris followed by some problems the solutions of which are provided at theend of the broschure. (RB) With 9 figs., 9 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>